docs.text: Welcome to Maja Gamma Labs Welcome to the site of Maja Gamma Labs. Maja Gamma labs was founded west of Patuki after the Great Balla Wars. When Nikku came home to Patuki from the Great Balla Wars he decided to set up Maja Gama Labs in the basement of his fathers workshop in D-chowk.
